[color=white]Campaign Presets:[/color] One-click campaign creation with pre-configured crew, resources, and progression.

[color=white]Phase Access:[/color] Jump directly to any campaign phase without navigation.

[color=white]Test Scenarios:[/color] Set up specific testing situations like rival attacks or resource crises.

[color=white]Save States:[/color] Quickly save and restore test configurations.

[color=yellow]Press F12 for debug console (when implemented)[/color]
[color=yellow]Press F1-F4 for quick save slots (when implemented)[/color]"

